Children expect new clothes, shoes, toys and a lot of (unhealthy) food. Relatives, too, often feel entitled to money and goodies from their kin.
"Send me Christmas," they will say when they call under the guise of checking up on you. Black Tax is usually paid in advance. Nobody expects anyone to be a Christmas grinch.



